  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nPresently the Lighthouse slasher is like a greedy dragon, hoarding all of its precious slashings in the Lighthouse op pool and never sharing them with the rest of the network. We should add a flag like `--slasher-broadcast` or `--slasher-altruistic` that enables broadcasting attestations for the health of the ~kingdom~ network.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nv1.0.3\r\n",
